    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阳间已彻底腐败，一场风暴即将改变世界秩序。发起这场风暴的就是您：一名强大的亡灵巫师，视死亡如无物，率领亡灵军团征战。教士与领主就算躲在堡垒高墙之后，也无法逃过您的怒火。击败数以百计的挡路者，让他们变成工具，实现更宏大的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Unliving》是一款包含战略元素的动态 Rogue-lite 型动作角色扮演游戏。召唤亡灵、使用多种咒语，探索以黑暗奢华像素艺术描绘的神秘世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将敌人转化成您的亡灵军队</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能让每个倒下的敌人复活并加入您的军队，组成无限规模的亡灵军团。重获新生的生物会有专属的独特能力。举例来说，生前拥有赐福能力的亡灵祭司，死而复活后会诅咒您的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/eae190382b5f7d4418f701056935eaca.poster.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/eae190382b5f7d4418f701056935eaca.webm?t=1762941302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开亡灵术的秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不论敌友，认识个性鲜明的角色群。审问您自己的亡灵邪教成员、逼供敌人，甚至与自己的命匣对话，逐一搜集亡灵巫师失落的记忆，揭开他长生不死的真相。谁知道，也许您会挖掘出教会最高层的残酷真相</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/279b3ba0f1cfe3763a3d97b61cdc53b6.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击溃所有挡路者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有部分生者是无助的弱者，其他都会反击您的势力。他们会坚守阵地，成群行动，且拥有强大的能力。珍惜生命的他们不好对付，因此您必须充分发挥亡灵领主的天赋，才能击倒他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/9964ba88b738347a9e1b7b368a03f026.poster.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/9964ba88b738347a9e1b7b368a03f026.webm?t=1762941302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征服未知土地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游玩都会随机生成一个世界，里面包含丰富多样的生物、宝物、秘密房间和致命陷阱。世界中的每个区域都有多样的生者居民，您可以侵入村庄，杀死软弱的农民扩充军队，也可以在沼泽中与强大的敌人决一死战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/66285d45d28409ebe3a639701af75320.poster.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/66285d45d28409ebe3a639701af75320.webm?t=1762941302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对战史诗级魔王</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个暗黑世界的强大生物会尽一切所能阻止您。每个魔王都有独特的战斗风格和能力，您必须善用作战技巧和战略思维，才有机会在血战中取得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/b71a92e620b4a2cc2684a3805167a798.poster.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/b71a92e620b4a2cc2684a3805167a798.webm?t=1762941302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死而复生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拒绝死亡的能力是亡灵巫师最大的秘密。受到致命一击对于亡灵巫师来说只是小小挫折。从死亡中汲取教训，不要以同样的方式再次败在敌人手上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/bb167825d7aa9b2b5f94aa9a1c65370a.poster.avif?t=1762941302\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986040/extras/bb167825d7aa9b2b5f94aa9a1c65370a.webm?t=1762941302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
